      "writtenOn": "2016-09-20T21:38:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you mind adding a glog.Warningf if t.Created.Before(j.Created)? If that happens, it\u0027s possible that we\u0027ll set the wrong status when the task scrolls out of the TaskCache window before the job scrolls out of the JobCache window. (Probably being too paranoid, but I can imagine future changes may violate this assumption.)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 1197,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 1197,
        "endChar": 25
      },
      "revId": "04c060e744893d1ae215a47f098d8cd279cc7186",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
